doing wandering around here?

00:07:42.729 --> 00:07:45.065
Not sure
but we'd better hurry up.

00:07:45.065 --> 00:07:47.400
If you control electricity,
you control the world.

00:07:49.336 --> 00:07:51.871
Our ticket
to a high‐voltage future.

00:07:51.871 --> 00:07:53.940
Right, we can lure Pikachu in

00:07:53.940 --> 00:07:56.142
using the stolen electricity
and then we'll catch it.

00:07:56.142 --> 00:07:57.510
Perfect.

00:07:57.510 --> 00:07:59.212
And goal!

00:07:59.212 --> 00:08:00.547
Yay!

00:08:00.547 --> 00:08:01.281
[AGREEMENT]

00:08:05.085 --> 00:08:07.354
