This is the system control room
I designed myself.

00:08:09.556 --> 00:08:12.192
Clemont. What a nice surprise.

00:08:12.192 --> 00:08:14.594
I'm sorry to barge in
but I was wondering

00:08:14.594 --> 00:08:16.096
may I show
all my friends around?

00:08:16.096 --> 00:08:19.432
Of course.
It's no problem at all.

00:08:19.432 --> 00:08:22.569
[all gasp]
Status report.

00:08:22.569 --> 00:08:24.938
There's a problem with
the transmission cables.

00:08:24.938 --> 00:08:27.140
‐ 'Near the transformer.'
‐ Transformer?

00:08:27.140 --> 00:08:28.808
That doesn't sound good.

00:08:28.808 --> 00:08:30.276
Just what are you
referring to?

00:08:30.276 --> 00:08:32.479
WORKER A
'Well, uh, the thing is,

00:08:32.479 --> 00:08:34.080
a wild Pokémon'

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:35.515
'has been making
its home there.'

00:08:35.515 --> 00:08:37.917
‐ Wild Pokémon?'
‐ 'Yes.'

00:08:37.917 --> 00:08:40.387
When we approach, it attacks.

00:08:40.387 --> 00:08:43.023
So we're kind of at a loss.

00:08:43.023 --> 00:08:45.058
It's okay.
I'll go and have a look.

00:08:45.058 --> 00:08:48.461
‐ Please, let me come with you.
‐ Yeah, I'll go too.

00:08:48.461 --> 00:08:50.330
[AGREEMENT]
Since you're the designer

00:08:50.330 --> 00:08:52.065
we value your opinions.

00:08:52.065 --> 00:08:53.700
Give us some feedback.

00:08:53.700 --> 00:08:55.769
I want you to wait here
for me, Bonnie.

00:08:55.769 --> 00:08:57.103
Will you keep an eye
on her, please?

00:08:57.103 --> 00:08:59.139
Mm‐hmm. Count on me.

