[CONCERNED]

00:09:04.377 --> 00:09:06.079
It's at the end
of that passageway.

00:09:06.079 --> 00:09:08.148
Come on, what's the holdup?

00:09:08.148 --> 00:09:10.417
It's a bit trickier
than I thought.

00:09:10.417 --> 00:09:13.053
Hey. Who's in there?
[gasps]

00:09:13.053 --> 00:09:14.921
Team Rocket.
What are you doing here?

00:09:14.921 --> 00:09:16.856
[ANGRY]
I think we'd better

00:09:16.856 --> 00:09:18.258
make like a tree and leave!

00:09:18.258 --> 00:09:20.727
[AGREEMENT]
