have to rethink our strategy.

00:10:45.378 --> 00:10:47.046
We'll retool,
then send the Twerps back

00:10:47.046 --> 00:10:48.448
to Team Rocket school.

00:10:48.448 --> 00:10:49.249
[AGREEMENT]

00:10:52.952 --> 00:10:54.521
ECLAIRISSE
'Team Rocket?'

00:10:54.521 --> 00:10:56.356
