who like to steal

00:10:56.356 --> 00:10:58.291
other people's stuff
and Pokémon too.

00:10:58.291 --> 00:10:59.959
[AGREEMENT]

00:10:59.959 --> 00:11:02.662
So they wanna steal
the town's electricity.

00:11:02.662 --> 00:11:04.964
Then we're going to have
to stop them.

00:11:04.964 --> 00:11:06.666
They're stubborn.
I'm sure they'll be back.

00:11:06.666 --> 00:11:08.968
That's for sure.

00:11:08.968 --> 00:11:10.904
They've caused an awful lot of
trouble for us in the past.

00:11:10.904 --> 00:11:12.205
Right, Clemont?

00:11:14.541 --> 00:11:16.976
‐ Clemont, wake up.
‐ Huh?

00:11:16.976 --> 00:11:19.879
Yes, right.
They're troublemakers.

00:11:19.879 --> 00:11:23.049
Well, hmm, we need
to come up with a plan.

00:11:23.049 --> 00:11:25.051
We'll have to be
on full alert.

00:11:25.051 --> 00:11:26.819
I'll let Officer Jenny know
what's going on.

00:11:34.894 --> 00:11:36.896
There. All pretty now.

00:11:36.896 --> 00:11:38.031
[HAPPY]

00:11:40.300 --> 00:11:41.901
Okay, Fennekin, you're next.

00:11:41.901 --> 00:11:43.169
[HAPPY]

00:11:45.138 --> 00:11:47.140
Clemont? What's bothering you?

00:11:47.140 --> 00:11:49.209
[CURIOUS]

00:11:49.209 --> 00:11:52.111
Uh, well, I was
just thinking about Shinx.

00:11:52.111 --> 00:11:54.414
Oh, Shinx.

00:11:54.414 --> 00:11:56.883
You mean that Pokémon you helped
when you went to school here?

00:11:56.883 --> 00:11:58.151
It's probably still here
in this town.

00:11:58.151 --> 00:12:00.053
[AGREEMENT]

