Huh?

00:12:02.722 --> 00:12:05.058
I never finished the story
I told you.

00:12:05.058 --> 00:12:07.026
It was the day
before my graduation.

00:12:07.026 --> 00:12:09.996
Something bad happened.

00:12:09.996 --> 00:12:12.232
Shinx and I had a
regular meeting place.

00:12:12.232 --> 00:12:14.367
I was on my way
to thank Shinx for the idea

00:12:14.367 --> 00:12:16.703
that led me
to my graduation research.

00:12:16.703 --> 00:12:19.172
This cake is decorated
with lots of berries

00:12:19.172 --> 00:12:21.608
for just the right amount
of sweetness.

00:12:21.608 --> 00:12:25.445
There's no doubt Shinx
is going to adore it.

00:12:25.445 --> 00:12:28.248
Then I'll ask Shinx
to become my partner.

00:12:28.248 --> 00:12:30.250
And travel along with me
back to Lumiose City.

00:12:33.553 --> 00:12:36.756
‐ Oh, it's Clemont.
‐ Hello, Mr. Mayor.

00:12:36.756 --> 00:12:38.558
I've been looking all over
for you and here you are.

00:12:38.558 --> 00:12:40.560
Huh?

00:12:40.560 --> 00:12:42.629
We've arranged a very
special dinner for you

00:12:42.629 --> 00:12:44.364
to help celebrate
your graduation.

00:12:44.364 --> 00:12:45.898
Please, get in.

00:12:45.898 --> 00:12:48.301
‐ But, Mr. Mayor‐‐
‐ Quick.

00:12:48.301 --> 00:12:51.004
The whole town is waiting
for you at the restaurant.

00:12:51.004 --> 00:12:53.573
Time's a‐wasting.
Come on, let's go.

00:12:53.573 --> 00:12:55.375
But, but, Mr. Mayor..

00:12:57.777 --> 00:12:58.711
Alright.

00:13:02.482 --> 00:13:03.449
Uh.

00:13:05.218 --> 00:13:06.052
CLEMONT
'Shinx.'

00:13:11.124 --> 00:13:14.127
As soon as I could, I hurried
back there after dinner

00:13:14.127 --> 00:13:16.229
but Shinx wasn't anywhere
to be found.

00:13:16.229 --> 00:13:18.898
And after that,
I never saw Shinx again.

00:13:18.898 --> 00:13:21.567
‐ I get it.
‐ Hey.

00:13:21.567 --> 00:13:24.370
When Shinx evolves,
it becomes Luxio, right?

00:13:24.370 --> 00:13:26.406
So, could that Luxio
possibly be..

00:13:26.406 --> 00:13:29.075
Luxio? It evolved?

00:13:29.075 --> 00:13:31.244
Maybe it evolved from the Shinx
that was your friend.

00:13:31.244 --> 00:13:33.746
Well, maybe I'm wrong.

00:13:33.746 --> 00:13:37.350
Remember, that Luxio didn't even
respond to you, Clemont.

00:13:37.350 --> 00:13:38.885
CLEMONT
'No. Your hypothesis

00:13:38.885 --> 00:13:40.286
is probably correct.'

00:13:40.286 --> 00:13:41.954
ASH/BONNIE
Huh?

00:13:41.954 --> 00:13:43.656
Yeah, looking into Luxio's
eyes..

00:13:48.261 --> 00:13:51.297
No doubt. It's the same Pokémon.

00:13:51.297 --> 00:13:54.167
That Luxio has to be my friend
Shinx after it evolved.

00:13:54.167 --> 00:13:56.736
No way.
[SHOCKED]

00:13:56.736 --> 00:13:58.004
I never showed up
at our meeting place

00:13:58.004 --> 00:14:00.406
that day like I promised.

00:14:00.406 --> 00:14:03.209
So Shinx must have thought
I abandoned it.

00:14:03.209 --> 00:14:04.344
'That's why..'

00:14:07.980 --> 00:14:10.583
‐ Huh?
‐ Oh no, it's a blackout.

00:14:10.583 --> 00:14:13.219
Clemont, this is awful.

00:14:13.219 --> 00:14:15.655
A huge amount of electricity has
been drained from the system.

00:14:15.655 --> 00:14:17.123
I'll bet
it's Team Rocket again.

00:14:17.123 --> 00:14:18.091
[ANGRY]

00:14:23.262 --> 00:14:24.897
[SURPRISED]

00:14:26.733 --> 00:14:27.967
[EXERTION]

00:14:33.306 --> 00:14:35.675
There's nothing like getting
electricity at no cost.

00:14:35.675 --> 00:14:37.677
And what could be
freer than free?

00:14:37.677 --> 00:14:40.713
[AGREEMENT]
[ATTACK]

00:14:40.713 --> 00:14:42.348
[screaming]

00:14:43.683 --> 00:14:46.452
[EXERTION]
Why you little pest.

00:14:46.452 --> 00:14:48.621
We've had about enough
out of you.

00:14:48.621 --> 00:14:50.456
And that's your cue, Pumpkaboo.

00:14:52.558 --> 00:14:53.826
[APPEARING]

00:14:53.826 --> 00:14:54.794
Inkay, you too.

00:14:56.396 --> 00:14:58.831
[APPEARING]

00:14:58.831 --> 00:15:01.267
I told the townspeople that they
should stay inside their homes

00:15:01.267 --> 00:15:03.770
until this whole issue
is solved.

00:15:03.770 --> 00:15:07.073
Also according to Officer Jenny,
they found no one below ground.

00:15:07.073 --> 00:15:08.708
But where did Team Rocket go?

00:15:08.708 --> 00:15:10.510
They were able to drain

00:15:10.510 --> 00:15:12.545
all of the town's electricity
at once somehow.

00:15:13.980 --> 00:15:14.647
Hey, I've got it.

00:15:17.483 --> 00:15:18.785
PUMPKABOO/INKAY
[ATTACK]

00:15:20.153 --> 00:15:21.354
Shadow Ball.

00:15:21.354 --> 00:15:23.756
[SHADOW BALL MOVE]

00:15:23.756 --> 00:15:25.258
[PAINED]

00:15:26.726 --> 00:15:28.428
[panting]

00:15:28.428 --> 00:15:29.462
Luxio.

00:15:31.130 --> 00:15:33.099
Team Rocket,
there you are.

00:15:33.099 --> 00:15:35.768
We won't allow you
to steal any more electricity.

00:15:35.768 --> 00:15:38.137
Prepare for trouble,
how pompous is that?

00:15:38.137 --> 00:15:40.840
And make it double,
it's tit for tat.

00:15:40.840 --> 00:15:43.209
To protect the world
from devastation.

00:15:43.209 --> 00:15:45.945
To unite all people
within our nation.

00:15:45.945 --> 00:15:49.048
To denounce the evils
of all your rules.

00:15:49.048 --> 00:15:52.385
To shut down the power
on arrogant schools.

00:15:52.385 --> 00:15:54.787
‐ Jessie.
‐ And James.

00:15:54.787 --> 00:15:57.890
Team Rocket blasts off
at the speed of light.

00:15:57.890 --> 00:15:59.892
Surrender now or prepare
for a lights‐out fight.

00:15:59.892 --> 00:16:01.527
Meowth, that's right.

00:16:01.527 --> 00:16:03.162
[AGREEMENT]

00:16:04.530 --> 00:16:07.300
[ATTACK]

00:16:09.902 --> 00:16:12.939
No way, Inkay.
I call Foul Play.

00:16:12.939 --> 00:16:16.275
[FOUL PLAY MOVE]
[PAINED]

00:16:16.275 --> 00:16:18.377
Pumpkaboo, Shadow Ball.

00:16:18.377 --> 00:16:20.613
[SHADOW BALL MOVE]
Pikachu, use Electro Ball!

00:16:20.613 --> 00:16:22.982
[AGREEMENT]/[ELECTRO BALL MOVE]

00:16:25.618 --> 00:16:27.854
[panting]

00:16:27.854 --> 00:16:29.522
Don't worry, Luxio.

00:16:29.522 --> 00:16:31.524
Just stay down
and we'll take care of this.

00:16:31.524 --> 00:16:33.559
[STRUGGLING]
Why do you insist on

00:16:33.559 --> 00:16:35.127
battling with Team Rocket?

00:16:35.127 --> 00:16:36.762
[DETERMINED]

00:16:39.365 --> 00:16:41.701
Dig this, Luxio wants a town

00:16:41.701 --> 00:16:44.070
where all Pokémon
can live happily.

00:16:44.070 --> 00:16:46.706
It's protecting the place the
science Twerp helped change.

00:16:46.706 --> 00:16:50.243
Where all Pokémon
can live happily? Huh?

00:16:50.243 --> 00:16:53.112
I wanna make a town where
Electric‐types can live happily.

00:16:53.112 --> 00:16:55.748
No, a world where all Pokémon
can live happily.

00:16:55.748 --> 00:16:57.650
That would be my dream
come true.

00:16:57.650 --> 00:16:59.919
‐ Ah, Luxio.
‐ The nerve.

00:16:59.919 --> 00:17:02.588
‐ How pompous.
‐ Finish this with Shadow Ball.

00:17:02.588 --> 00:17:04.924
[SHADOW BALL MOVE]
Look out!

00:17:04.924 --> 00:17:06.993
[CONCERNED]/[SHOCKED]

00:17:06.993 --> 00:17:08.127
Clemont, no.

00:17:08.961 --> 00:17:11.264
[groaning]

00:17:11.264 --> 00:17:13.366
Thank goodness you're okay.
Hmm.

00:17:13.366 --> 00:17:15.167
[AWARE]

00:17:15.167 --> 00:17:16.536
[grunting]

00:17:16.536 --> 00:17:17.937
[screams]

00:17:17.937 --> 00:17:19.772
[groans]
[EXCITED]

00:17:21.073 --> 00:17:23.209
[sighs]
[HAPPY]

00:17:23.209 --> 00:17:24.143
[CHUCKLE]

00:17:25.378 --> 00:17:27.046
[snoring]

00:17:29.482 --> 00:17:30.550
[HAPPY]

00:17:31.284 --> 00:17:32.218
[sighs]

00:17:35.154 --> 00:17:36.856
[GASP]

00:17:39.392 --> 00:17:41.994
Huh?
[LICKING]

00:17:41.994 --> 00:17:44.864
Huh? Luxio.

00:17:44.864 --> 00:17:46.699
We got the juice,
so time to cut loose.

00:17:46.699 --> 00:17:48.501
Now, for Pikachu.

00:17:48.501 --> 00:17:49.735
You're coming with us
without an excuse.

00:17:49.735 --> 00:17:51.871
[AGREEMENT]

00:17:51.871 --> 00:17:55.107
[grunts]
Okay, Inkay. Use Psybeam.

00:17:55.107 --> 00:17:56.976
Now, Pumpkaboo, Dark Pulse.

00:17:56.976 --> 00:17:58.778
INKAY/PUMPKABOO
[PSYBEAM MOVE]/[DARK PULSE MOVE]

00:17:58.778 --> 00:18:01.380
Thunderbolt!
[THUNDERBOLT MOVE]

00:18:02.915 --> 00:18:03.983
[grunts]

00:18:06.519 --> 00:18:08.888
Hmm. Luxio, would you please
stand and battle with me?

00:18:08.888 --> 00:18:10.957
[AGREEMENT]
[gasps]

00:18:10.957 --> 00:18:13.225
Great. Use Discharge.

00:18:13.225 --> 00:18:14.594
[AGREEMENT]/[DISCHARGE MOVE]

00:18:16.295 --> 00:18:20.366
[PAINED]
[screaming]

00:18:20.366 --> 00:18:22.034
JESSIE
'School's out.'

00:18:22.034 --> 00:18:24.236
JESSIE/JAMES/MEOWTH
We're blasting off again.

00:18:24.236 --> 00:18:26.038
WOBBUFFET/INKAY
[AGREEMENT]

00:18:28.307 --> 00:18:29.809
We did it. We did it.
We did it.

00:18:29.809 --> 00:18:31.143
[cheering]

00:18:37.583 --> 00:18:39.518
Luxio.

00:18:39.518 --> 00:18:42.588
Hmm. Please, wait.

00:18:46.392 --> 00:18:48.961
Luxio, I'd really like you
to come with me.

00:18:53.265 --> 00:18:54.967
I remember.

00:18:54.967 --> 00:18:56.936
I gave you my word,
then let you down.

00:18:58.638 --> 00:19:01.874
But now,
I'll be waiting for you.

00:19:01.874 --> 00:19:04.910
At the same place
and at the exact same time.

00:19:04.910 --> 00:19:06.879
CLEMONT
'So, if you decide

00:19:06.879 --> 00:19:09.415
to come with me'
'meet me in the square.'

00:19:13.519 --> 00:19:14.487
Hmm.

00:19:28.234 --> 00:19:30.236
I don't see Luxio anywhere.

00:19:30.236 --> 00:19:32.371
I guess that means
it's still mad.

00:19:32.371 --> 00:19:34.306
[SAD]

00:19:34.306 --> 00:19:36.275
Luxio will show up.

00:19:36.275 --> 00:19:37.877
We've gotta give it
a little more time.

00:19:37.877 --> 00:19:39.278
[AGREEMENT]

00:19:39.278 --> 00:19:41.714
‐ No.
‐ Huh?

00:19:41.714 --> 00:19:44.350
I guess that Luxio
still hasn't forgiven me

00:19:44.350 --> 00:19:45.818
which is all that I deserve.

00:19:45.818 --> 00:19:47.553
It's time to go.

00:19:47.553 --> 00:19:49.855
If I stay here any longer

00:19:49.855 --> 00:19:52.124
it won't be fair
to the rest of you.

00:19:52.124 --> 00:19:53.459
Hmm.
Let's get back on the road.

00:19:56.262 --> 00:19:57.830
[all groaning]

00:19:57.830 --> 00:19:58.164
ECLAIRISSE/ASH/BONNIE/SERENA
Huh?

00:20:03.602 --> 00:20:04.670
Huh?

00:20:09.508 --> 00:20:11.777
You came back after all.

00:20:11.777 --> 00:20:12.845
Luxio.

00:20:14.480 --> 00:20:16.115
[HAPPY]

00:20:16.115 --> 00:20:17.550
[all gasping]

00:20:17.550 --> 00:20:19.685
Wow. Okay, here goes.

00:20:19.685 --> 00:20:21.053
Go Poké Ball.

00:20:27.093 --> 00:20:28.961
Alright.

00:20:28.961 --> 00:20:31.330
Today's a great day,
thanks to science.

00:20:31.330 --> 00:20:33.966
‐ I caught Luxio.
‐ Yay. That's my big brother.

00:20:33.966 --> 00:20:37.703
Alright.

00:20:37.703 --> 00:20:41.207
Thank you, Luxio.
I won't let you down.

00:20:41.207 --> 00:20:44.009
NARRATOR
And so, two old friends reunite

00:20:44.009 --> 00:20:47.313
as Luxio becomes the newest
member of our heroes' family

00:20:47.313 --> 00:20:50.049
but their quest to meet new
people and new Pokémon

00:20:50.049 --> 00:20:52.184
will go on
as the journey continues.

